<p data-start="261" data-end="432">But <strong data-start="265" data-end="311">your PostgreSQL table is still the old one</strong>. SQLAlchemy's <code data-start="326" data-end="343">db.create_all()</code> <strong data-start="344" data-end="379">does not modify existing tables</strong>. It only creates tables if they don't already exist.</p>
