    </span><span class="ͼ11">db</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>create_all()</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="274" data-end="354">will automatically create a <strong data-start="302" data-end="328">new <code data-start="308" data-end="320">candidates</code> table</strong> with the updated columns:</p>
<ul data-start="356" data-end="465">
<li data-start="356" data-end="362">
<p data-start="358" data-end="362"><code data-start="358" data-end="362">id</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="363" data-end="371">
<p data-start="365" data-end="371"><code data-start="365" data-end="371">name</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="372" data-end="381">
<p data-start="374" data-end="381"><code data-start="374" data-end="381">email</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="382" data-end="391">
<p data-start="384" data-end="391"><code data-start="384" data-end="391">phone</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="392" data-end="402">
<p data-start="394" data-end="402"><code data-start="394" data-end="402">degree</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="403" data-end="418">
<p data-start="405" data-end="418"><code data-start="405" data-end="418">institution</code></p>
</li>
