ir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="77">Congratulations! 🎉 Your Resume Parser ATS is ready to be uploaded to GitHub.</p>
<h2 data-start="79" data-end="116">Step 1: Create a GitHub repository</h2>
<ol data-start="118" data-end="393">
<li data-start="118" data-end="149">
<p data-start="121" data-end="149">Go to <strong data-start="127" data-end="149"><a data-start="129" data-end="147" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/">https://github.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="150" data-end="206">
<p data-start="153" data-end="206">Click the <strong data-start="163" data-end="168">+</strong> icon (top-right) → <strong data-start="188" data-end="206">New repository</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="207" data-end="261">
<p data-start="210" data-end="226">Repository name:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="230" data-end="261"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>resume-parser-ats</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-start="262" data-end="283">
<p data-start="265" data-end="283">Make it <strong data-start="273" data-end="283">Public</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="284" data-end="361">
<p data-start="287" data-end="361"><strong data-start="287" data-end="297">Do not</strong> initialize it with a README (since you already have a project).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="362" data-end="393">
<p data-start="365" data-end="393">Click <strong data-start="371" data-end="392">Create repository</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="395" data-end="398">
