ll flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="157">The error confirms <strong data-start="19" data-end="46">Windows cannot find Git</strong>. At this point, don't keep trying <code data-start="81" data-end="86">git</code> commands—they won't work until Git is installed or your PATH is fixed.</p>
<h3 data-start="159" data-end="201">Step 1: Check whether Git is installed</h3>
<p data-start="203" data-end="263">Open <strong data-start="208" data-end="225">File Explorer</strong> and look for either of these folders:</p>
<ul data-start="265" data-end="320">
<li data-start="265" data-end="289">
<p data-start="267" data-end="289"><code data-start="267" data-end="289">C:\Program Files\Git</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="290" data-end="320">
<p data-start="292" data-end="320"><code data-start="292" data-end="320">C:\Program Files (x86)\Git</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 data-start="322" data-end="351">If neither folder exists</h4>
<p data-start="352" data-end="377">Git is <strong data-start="359" data-end="376">not installed</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="379" data-end="396">Download it from:</p>
<p data-start="398" data-end="434"><strong data-start="398" data-end="434"><a data-start="400" data-end="432" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://git-scm.com/download/win">https://git-scm.com/download/win<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong></p>
<p data-start="436" data-end="539">Install it with the default options (make sure the option to use Git from the command line is enabled).</p>
<p data-start="541" data-end="560">After installation:</p>
<ol data-start="561" data-end="609">
<li data-start="561" data-end="578">
<p data-start="564" data-end="578">Close VS Code.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="579" data-end="601">
<p data-start="582" data-end="601">Open VS Code again.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="602" data-end="609">
<p data-start="605" data-end="609">Run:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="611" data-end="642"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PowerShell</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div c