lass="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">commit</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">-</span><span class="ͼ11">m</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"Initial Resume Parser ATS"</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="453" data-end="488">If Git asks for your identity, run:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="490" data-end="671"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PowerShell</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">config</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">--</span><span class="ͼ11">global</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">user</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼ11">name</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"Your Name"</span><span>

</span><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">config</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">--</span><span class="ͼ11">global</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">user</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼ11">email</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"youremail@example.com"</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="673" data-end="718">Replace them with your GitHub name and email.</p>
<hr data-start="720" data-end="723">
<h2 data-start="725" data-end="762">Step 4: Create a GitHub repository</h2>
<p data-start="764" data-end="770">Go to:</p>
<p data-start="772" data-end="798"><strong data-start="772" data-end="798"><a data-start="774" data-end="796" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/new">https://github.com/new<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong></p>
<p data-start="800" data-end="816">Repository name:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="818" data-end="843"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>resume-parser-ats</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="845" data-end="907">Make it <strong data-start="853" data-end="863">Public</strong> and <strong data-start="868" data-end="878">do not</strong> initialize it with a README.</p>
<p data-start="909" data-end="937">Click <strong data-start="915" data-end="936">Create repository</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="939" data-end="942">
<h2 data-start="944" data-end="981">Step 5: Connect your local project</h2>
<p data-start="983" data-end="1042">After creating the repository, GitHub will show a URL like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1044" data-end="1106"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/resume-parser-ats.git</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1108" data-end="1112">Run:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1114" data-end="1352"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PowerShell</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">remote</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">add</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">origin</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">https</span><span class="ͼv">://</span><span class="ͼ11">github</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼ11">com</span><span class="ͼv">/</span><span class="ͼ11">YOUR_USERNAME</span><span class="ͼv">/</span><span class="ͼ11">resume-parser-ats</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼ11">git</span><span>

</span><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">branch</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">-</span><span class="ͼ11">M</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">main</span><span>

</span><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">push</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">-</span><span class="ͼ11">u</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">origin</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">main</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1354" data-end="1404">Replace <code data-start="1362" data-end="1377">YOUR_USERNAME</code> with your GitHub username.</p>
<hr data-start="1406" data-end="1409">
<h2 data-start="1411" data-end="1452">(Recommended) Fix Git PATH permanently</h2>
<p data-start="1454" data-end="1508">So you can simply type <code data-start="1477" data-end="1482">git</code> instead of the full path:</p>
<ol data-start="1510" data-end="1707">
<li data-start="1510" data-end="1586">
<p data-start="1513" data-end="1586">Press <strong data-start="1519" data-end="1526">Win</strong> and search for <strong data-start="1542" data-end="1585">"Edit the system environment variables"</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1587" data-end="1622">
<p data-start="1590" data-end="1622">Click <strong data-start="1596" data-end="1621">Environment Variables</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1623" data-end="1681">
<p data-start="1626" data-end="1681">Under <strong data-start="1632" data-end="1652">System variables</strong>, select <strong data-start="1661" data-end="1669">Path</strong> → <strong data-start="1672" data-end="1680">Edit</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1682" data-end="1707">
<p data-start="1685" data-end="1707">Click <strong data-start="1691" data-end="1698">New</strong> and add:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1709" data-end="1741"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>C:\Program Files\Git\cmd</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="5" data-start="1743" data-end="1806">
<li data-start="1743" data-end="1774">
<p data-start="1746" data-end="1774">Click <strong data-start="1752" data-end="1758">OK</strong> on all windows.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1775" data-end="1806">
<p data-start="1778" data-end="1806">Close and reopen PowerShell.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1808" data-end="1829">Now this should work:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1831" data-end="1862"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PowerShell</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div