<hr data-start="827" data-end="830">
<h3 data-start="832" data-end="857">2. Improve the README</h3>
<p data-start="859" data-end="886">Your README should include:</p>
<ul data-start="888" data-end="1009">
<li data-start="888" data-end="909">
