</li>
<li data-start="969" data-end="987">
<p data-start="971" data-end="987">Folder structure</p>
</li>
<li data-start="988" data-end="1009">
<p data-start="990" data-end="1009">Future improvements</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1011" data-end="1061">A polished README makes a strong first impression.</p>
<hr data-start="1063" data-end="1066">
<h3 data-start="1068" data-end="1090">3. Add screenshots</h3>
<p data-start="1092" data-end="1112">Take screenshots of:</p>
<ul data-start="1113" data-end="1187">
<li data-start="1113" data-end="1124">
<p data-start="1115" data-end="1124">Home page</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1125" data-end="1138">
<p data-start="1127" data-end="1138">Upload page</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1139" data-end="1150">
<p data-start="1141" data-end="1150">Dashboard</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1151" data-end="1170">
<p data-start="1153" data-end="1170">Candidate details</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1171" data-end="1187">
<p data-start="1173" data-end="1187">Search results</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1189" data-end="1205">Create a folder:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1207" data-end="1227"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>screenshots/</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1229" data-end="1263">and reference them in your README.</p>
<hr data-start="1265" data-end="1268">
<h3 data-start="1270" data-end="1290">4. Add a license</h3>
<p data-start="1292" data-end="1312">Create a file named:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1314" data-end="1329"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>LICENSE</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1331" data-end="1395">Use the <strong data-start="1339" data-end="1354">MIT License</strong> unless your college specifies otherwise.</p>
<hr data-start="1397" data-end="1400">
