<ol start="6" data-start="448" data-end="478">
<li data-start="448" data-end="478">
<p data-start="451" data-end="478">Press <strong data-start="457" data-end="469">Ctrl + S</strong> to save.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="480" data-end="483">
<h2 data-start="485" data-end="514">Method 2: Using PowerShell</h2>
<p data-start="516" data-end="546">From your project folder, run:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="548" data-end="584"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PowerShell</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼ11">notepad</span><span> .</span><span class="ͼ11">gitignore</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="586" data-end="632">If prompted to create the file, click <strong data-start="624" data-end="631">Yes</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="634" data-end="640">Paste:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="642" data-end="697"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>gitignore</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
uploads/</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="699" data-end="722">Save and close Notepad.</p>
<hr data-start="724" data-end="727">
<h2 data-start="729" data-end="760">Remove already tracked files</h2>
<p data-start="762" data-end="879">Since you already pushed them to GitHub, <code data-start="803" data-end="815">.gitignore</code> alone is <strong data-start="825" data-end="839">not enough</strong>. You need to stop tracking those files.</p>
<p data-start="881" data-end="900">Run these commands:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="902" data-end="1099"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PowerShell</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ10">rm</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">-</span><span class="ͼ10">r</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">--</span><span class="ͼ11">cached</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">uploads</span><span>

</span><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ10">rm</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">-</span><span class="ͼ10">r</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">--</span><span class="ͼ11">cached</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">__pycache__</span><span>

</span><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ10">rm</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">--</span><span class="ͼ11">cached</span><span> .</span><span class="ͼ11">env</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1101" data-end="1106">Then:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1108" data-end="1301"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-(--code-block-surface)"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PowerShell</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">add</span><span> .

</span><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">commit</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">-</span><span class="ͼ11">m</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"Add .gitignore and remove ignored files"</span><span>

</span><span class="ͼv">&amp;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼz">"C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\git.exe"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">push</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1303" data-end="1313">This will:</p>
<ul data-start="1314" data-end="1423">
<li data-start="1314" data-end="1350">
<p data-start="1316" data-end="1350">✅ Keep the files on your computer.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1351" data-end="1379">
<p data-start="1353" data-end="1379">✅ Remove them from GitHub.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1380" data-end="1423">
<p data-start="1382" data-end="1423">✅ Prevent them from being uploaded again.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1425" data-end="1487" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, I can also <span class="entity-underline hover:entity-accent group inline cursor-pointer align-baseline whitespace-nowrap" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity: 1; width: 1.5rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="group-hover:entity-accent icon text-token-text-primary inline-block transition-transform duration-150 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-28b72de4.svg#e04414" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span><span class="group-hover:entity-accent whitespace-normal">help you make your GitHub repository look much more professional with a polished README, screenshots, and badges</span></span>.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-cen