le\":\"Make a rainy-trip packing guide\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light packing layout image for a rainy trip, with simple item icons and empty spaces I can tick or label myself.\"},{\"body\":\"For Rath Yatra 2026, explain the main terms, the chariot symbolism and what a first-time observer should know respectfully.\",\"title\":\"Learn Rath Yatra basics\"},{\"body\":\"Practise a behavioural interview answer with me using STAR. Ask me for the role and one experience, then coach my first draft.\",\"title\":\"Practise an interview answer\"},{\"title\":\"Make sapling care cards\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light Van Mahotsav sapling care card with icons for water, sun, pruning, and a blank plant name.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light monsoon bag map for my commute. Ask my city first, then make it simple, bright and printable.\",\"title\":\"Draw my monsoon bag map\"},{\"body\":\"Help me design a morning routine I can actually follow. Ask one question about my start time, then suggest a simple first week.\",\"title\":\"Design a morning routine\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple top-down desk layout with zones for work, charging and stationery. Use icons and blank labels, not tiny text.\",\"title\":\"Draw a calmer desk layout\"},{\"title\":\"Pack one bag without drama\",\"body\":\"Turn my trip packing into a one-bag game. Ask where I’m going and for how many days, then give a compact list with “skip it” notes.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a World Cup prediction game\",\"body\":\"Create a low-stakes FIFA World Cup prediction game for friends, with simple rules and a blank score table.\"},{\"body\":\"Plan a tomato-light Indian dinner. Give swaps for dal, sabzi and chutney, and ask what staples I have only if needed.\",\"title\":\"Cook with fewer tomatoes\"},{\"title\":\"Draw tomato-light swaps\",\"body\":\"Create a simple text-light kitchen card showing tomato-light swaps for dal, sabzi and chutney. Use icons and blank labels, no brand names.\"},{\"title\":\"Decode the monsoon map\",\"b