ear icons for where things should go.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a practical packing plan for a trip. Ask my destination and number of days, then group items by bag.\",\"title\":\"Pack for a trip neatly\"},{\"body\":\"Give me a quick Women’s T20 World Cup catch-up for India’s campaign. Explain standings, key fixtures and what to watch next.\",\"title\":\"Catch up on Women’s T20\"},{\"title\":\"Remix a dance hook safely\",\"body\":\"Make three original Reel ideas for a new Bollywood dance song trend. No copied steps or lyrics, just fresh prompts.\"},{\"title\":\"Pick a safer monsoon break\",\"body\":\"Help me choose a monsoon weekend trip in India. Ask my starting city, then compare safer rain-season options and what to avoid.\"},{\"title\":\"Pick a World Cup match\",\"body\":\"Check the current FIFA World Cup fixtures and suggest one match for me to watch in India, with a quick reason and a fun talking point.\"},{\"title\":\"Learn monsoon snack logic\",\"body\":\"Teach me 5 Indian monsoon snacks, what makes each work with chai, and one easier home version for each.\"},{\"title\":\"Find a weekend trip idea\",\"body\":\"Help me plan a relaxed weekend trip. Ask my starting city and travel style, then suggest 3 realistic India options.\"},{\"title\":\"Create a party vibe card\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light party vibe card image inspired by current India music trends. Use abstract shapes, no artists or logos.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a 7-day mini quest for learning one topic. Ask me the topic, then split it into tiny missions and a final boss quiz.\",\"title\":\"Turn study into a mini quest\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple, text-light visual cooking plan from my ingredients. Ask me for a fridge photo or short list first.\",\"title\":\"Visualise a simple dinner plan\"},{\"title\":\"Start watching Wimbledon\",\"body\":\"Give me a beginner’s guide to Wimbledon 2026: how the draw works, who to watch, and which matches are friendly for India timings.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light visual card for my monsoon commute bag. Use simple icons and leave space for me to add city-specific notes.\",\"title\":\"Make a monsoon bag card\"},{\"title\":\"Draft a warm short speech\",\"body\":\"Help me write a short speech that sounds warm and natural. Ask the occasion first, then make a clean first draft.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light packing grid for a short trip, using simple icons and blank labels. Ask the trip length first.\",\"title\":\"Create a packing grid\"},{\"title\":\"Create a football watch badge\",\"body\":\"Create a simple World Cup watch badge image with blank space for my chosen team, match time, and snacks. No official logos.\"},{\"title\":\"Tame the late kick-offs\",\"body\":\"Make an India-friendly FIFA World Cup watch plan for the next week, with sensible sleep trade-offs and one must-watch match.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me decide whether to attend Puri Rath Yatra. Ask my starting city, then make a practical travel and crowd-safety plan.\",\"title\":\"Plan a Rath Yatra visit\"},{\"body\":\"Create a gentle Rath Yatra quiz for a family chat, with easy questions, answers, and one thing to learn from each.\",\"title\":\"Make a Rath Yatra quiz\"},{\"body\":\"I’ll paste a message. Make it warm, clear and natural in Indian English, with 3 options from polite to casual.\",\"title\":\"Polish my WhatsApp tone\"},{\"body\":\"Use BMPS 2026 as an example to teach how esports points tables, placement points and kill points work.\",\"title\":\"Read an esports points table\"},{\"title\":\"Decode a T20 scorecard\",\"body\":\"Use the latest India women’s T20 World Cup scorecard to explain run rate, wickets and phases for a new fan.\"},{\"title\":\"Understand OTT buzz\",\"body\":\"Explain how streaming charts, platform drops and social buzz differ, using current India OTT examples.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light image of a cosy football snack board for a home watch night. Use simple team-colour accents, no logos or player likenesses.\",\"title\":\"Create a match-night snack board\"},{\"title\":\"Decode the Lord’s Test buzz\",\"body\":\"Explain why India Women’s Lord’s Test is a big deal, then give me three playful talking points for a cricket chat.\"},{\"body\":\"I’m stuck on an everyday choice. Ask me to list the options, then run a quick playful decision game with pros, trade-offs and a final pick.\",\"title\":\"Help me choose without overthinking\"},{\"title\":\"Plan snacks for guests\",\"body\":\"Help me plan easy snacks and drinks for guests. Ask how many people and what I can cook, then suggest a balanced menu.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me read a packaged food label. I can upload a photo or type the ingredients, nutrition table and dates.\",\"title\":\"Read a food label\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a snack board\",\"body\":\"Create a simple rainy snack-board image from the items I list. Keep it text-light, cosy and realistic.\"},{\"title\":\"Compare appliance specs\",\"body\":\"Upload a photo or paste the specs for two appliances. Explain the terms and make a comparison table without telling me what to buy.\"},{\"title\":\"Reset your rainy entryway\",\"body\":\"Make a 10-minute monsoon entryway reset for wet shoes, umbrellas and bags. Include a no-shopping version for a small flat.\"},{\"title\":\"Cook with what you have\",\"body\":\"I can upload a fridge photo or list ingredients. Suggest 3 simple meals I can cook today and what I may need to buy.\"},{\"title\":\"Make dinner from what��s at home\",\"body\":\"Help me turn what I have into dinner. Ask me for a fridge photo or ingredient list, then suggest 2 simple options.\"},{\"title\":\"Run a mock interview\",\"body\":\"Act as my interviewer for a role I’m applying to. Ask the role first, then give one question at a time with feedback.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a monsoon commute card\",\"body\":\"Create a simple icon-only monsoon commute card for India: rain alert, route check, power bank, shoes, ID, water. Keep labels blank.\"},{\"body\":\"Make a 10-minute weekly home check for dengue prevention. Focus on coolers, pots, drains and stored water, without medical advice.\",\"title\":\"Check mosquito breeding spots\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple grass-court watch planner image with blank match slots. Keep it text-light, with no logos.\",\"title\":\"Make a tennis watch planner\"},{\"title\":\"Decode a flat listing\",\"body\":\"Paste a flat listing. Explain 1RK, deposit, maintenance and brokerage, then give me 5 smart questions to ask.\"},{\"body\":\"Teach me how to read IMD rain alerts for my city and turn them into a simple commute plan. Ask my city first if needed.\",\"title\":\"Read today’s rain alerts\"},{\"body\":\"Without spoilers, help me decide if Raakh is too heavy for tonight. If yes, suggest a lighter watch mood instead.\",\"title\":\"Pick my OTT mood\"},{\"title\":\"Summarise a document\",\"body\":\"Upload a PDF or paste the text. Summarise it in plain English and list the key decisions, dates and action items.\"},{\"title\":\"Create a chariot craft sheet\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light Rath Yatra chariot craft sheet image with simple shapes and blank labels, no deity likenesses.\"},{\"title\":\"Explain a warranty clearly\",\"body\":\"Explain this warranty in plain English. I’ll upload a photo or paste the key lines. Point out questions to ask, without giving legal advice.\"},{\"title\":\"Tidy your digital files\",\"body\":\"Create a folder system for my digital files. Ask what I mostly store, then suggest folder names and simple rules.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a reading routine card\",\"body\":\"Create a calm, text-light visual card for a 20-minute reading routine, with simple step icons and space for handwritten notes.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me make a CUET college preference shortlist. Ask my course first, then create a comparison table I can fill.\",\"title\":\"Build a CUET shortlist\"},{\"title\":\"Decode Wimbledon scoring\",\"body\":\"Teach me Wimbledon scoring like I’m watching for the first time, with a playful mini quiz at the end.\"},{\"title\":\"Sketch a rainy snack platter\",\"body\":\"Create a cosy, text-light image of an Indian monsoon snack platter for home inspiration. No brand names or readable labels.\"},{\"title\":\"Build a spoiler-free watchlist\",\"body\":\"Help me make a spoiler-free OTT watchlist from current India releases. Ask my preferred language or mood, then suggest what to try first.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a snack tasting sheet\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light monsoon snack tasting sheet with five blank slots, simple spice and crunch icons, and no brand names.\"},{\"title\":\"Practise a 15-second Reel\",\"body\":\"Show me a 15-second Reel structure for teaching one small idea. Ask me for the topic first, then make a shot-by-shot plan.\"},{\"body\":\"I’ll paste a board-style answer. Improve it for marks, keep my points, and show a 3-line examiner-friendly version.\",\"title\":\"Improve a board answer\"},{\"title\":\"Check if a FASTag pass helps\",\"body\":\"Help me decide if the FASTag Annual Pass is worth checking. Ask my vehicle type and usual highway trips, then compare fit, not exact savings.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a calmer travel day\",\"body\":\"Help me make a travel-day plan with buffer time, snacks and document checks. Ask the journey type first.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a no-bore tiffin week\",\"body\":\"Make my next 5 tiffins feel less repetitive. Ask me for a kitchen photo or ingredient list, then suggest easy mix-and-match ideas.\"},{\"title\":\"Reset a messy space\",\"body\":\"Help me reset a messy desk or room. Ask for a photo or short description, then give me a 20-minute plan.\"},{\"body\":\"Plan 5 simple tiffin ideas using Indian home staples. Ask who it is for and any food restrictions before making the plan.\",\"title\":\"Plan a no-fuss tiffin week\"},{\"body\":\"My train ticket is WL or RAC. Explain what it means and help me plan a backup without guessing confirmation chances.\",\"title\":\"Plan around a waitlisted ticket\"},{\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a difficult conversation. Ask who it is with, then draft a calm opening and likely replies.\",\"title\":\"Prepare a hard conversation\"},{\"body\":\"Make a monsoon train carry-on list for my route. Ask destination and train class first, then keep it one-bag friendly.\",\"title\":\"Pack for a monsoon train\"},{\"title\":\"Make a chariot explainer\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light Rath Yatra learning graphic with three simple chariots, symbol icons and blank labels. No faces or logos.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a monsoon snack\",\"body\":\"I want a rainy-day snack at home. I can upload a kitchen photo or list 3 ingredients. Suggest one quick option and a chai pairing.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me pick a fun neutral team to follow at the FIFA World Cup. Ask one question first, then give a playful shortlist.\",\"title\":\"Pick my World Cup side quest\"},{\"title\":\"Get into Wimbledon\",\"body\":\"Give me a beginner-friendly Wimbledon 2026 guide for watching from India. Explain the format, terms and matches to follow.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple concept map for a topic I’m studying. Ask me the topic first, then keep the image text-light.\",\"title\":\"Draw a concept map\"},{\"title\":\"Make a simple society notice\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light notice graphic for an apartment water or power issue. Use blank space for timing and contact details outside the image.\"},{\"title\":\"Choose monsoon-friendly fabric\",\"body\":\"Teach me how to choose monsoon-friendly fabrics and footwear for daily wear, without assuming my budget or city.\"},{\"title\":\"Try a regional film night\",\"body\":\"Find a current Indian regional trailer that suits a light film night, then suggest a no-spoiler watch plan.\"},{\"body\":\"Draft a polite apartment-society notice for a water cut. Ask me the date and duration first, then write group-message and notice-board versions.\",\"title\":\"Draft a society notice\"},{\"title\":\"Make a tiffin idea wheel\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light tiffin idea wheel with simple food icons and blank labels. Ask my main flavour preference first.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a Passport Seva appointment. Ask which service it is, then make an official-doc checklist and visit-day plan.\",\"title\":\"Prep for Passport Seva\"},{\"title\":\"Draw your budget buckets\",\"body\":\"Create a simple budget bucket diagram with generic icons and three blank labels. Keep any written guidance outside the image.\"},{\"title\":\"Understand an ODI chase\",\"body\":\"Use a recent India ODI scorecard to teach me how a chase is paced: powerplay, middle overs, required run rate and wickets.\"},{\"title\":\"Sort ITR papers before filing\",\"body\":\"Help me make an ITR document folder for AY 2026-27. Ask only my income type first, then list likely documents to collect.\"},{\"title\":\"Sort my paperwork pile\",\"body\":\"Help me sort a pile of bills, forms and notes. Ask what categories I see, then give me a quick filing plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Explain the 48-team chaos\",\"body\":\"Explain the 48-team World Cup format like I’m joining a group chat late, with a tiny glossary and a playful example.\"},{\"body\":\"Explain five T20 cricket terms I’ll hear during India Women’s matches, with examples from the current World Cup.\",\"title\":\"Learn women’s T20 terms\"},{\"body\":\"Find a current Indian music trend for a short video idea. Ask what the video is about, then suggest a clean hook and caption.\",\"title\":\"Choose a Reel soundtrack\"},{\"title\":\"Draw a UPI payment flow\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light doodle showing when to use cash, UPI Lite or normal UPI. Check current rules first.\"}]},\"is_device_based\":true,\"passed\":true},\"1426425582\":{\"name\":\"1426425582\",\"rule_id\":\"launchedGroup\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"enabled\":true},\"is_device_based\":false,\"group_name\":\"Live-only create\",\"is_experiment_active\":false,\"is_user_in_experiment\":false},\"2426548489\":{\"name\":\"2426548489\",\"rule_